                                      .

   The City Manager for the city of Kelso is Doug Robinson (email address
       doug.robinson@ci.longview.wa.us) Betty Erickson (email address
            berickson@kelso.gov) is his Administrative Assistant.

    The primary responsibilities of the City Manager are to carry out the
     Kelso City Council's policies, prepare the city budget, direct the
    city's daily operations, coordinate the various departments and keep
                      the Kelso City Council informed.

   Additionally, many citizens will contact the City Manager to help solve
    a problem they may have involving services provided by the city. The
     City Manager's office hours are from 8:00 a.m. to 5:00 p.m., Monday
                               through Friday.

                  Address: 105 Allen Street Kelso, WA 98626
                   Phone: (360) 423-1371 or (360) 423-1719
                         Fax Number: (360) 423-1738


